<template id="website.homepage" name="Homepage" page="True" priority="29">
  <t t-call="website.layout">
    <div id="wrap" class="oe_structure oe_empty">
      <section class="oe_black mb0 mt0">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center mb128 mt128">
              <h2>You think hosting your applications does not worth your time?</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h1 class="text-center">About</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <img alt="Odoo image and text block" class="img img-responsive mb16 img-rounded" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/what-is-clouder.jpeg" style="animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <h3>What is Clouder?</h3>
              <p>Clouder is a group of Odoo modules which connect to your servers to easily create and maintain your own hosting infrastructure. Build by professionnals, wheter your are an hosting guru having all the infrastructure of your company on your shoulders or a geek newbie who want to deploy applications for his friends, you'll find in Clouder all you need : An open-source system which deploy the applications for you, using all the goods practices without you even knowing them.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <h3>The problem</h3>
              <p>Today, even if excellent opensources software exists, most peoples use closed-source internet services because they are convenient, and generally free. But then you become the product, losing your private life in the process and a part of your freedom. Even compagnies rarely hesitate to let go their confidential data, for convenience. This is happening because open-sources services are too difficult to install, not everyone can be an hosting guru and nobody can know how to host all applications on the Internet. We needed to do something.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <img alt="Odoo text and image block" class="img img-responsive mb16 img-rounded" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/gafa_logo.png" style="animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <img alt="Odoo image and text block" class="img img-responsive mb16 img-rounded" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/helping-each-other.jpg" style="height: 20em; text-align: center; animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mt16">
              <h3>Our solution</h3>
              <p>The key point is, this is not because you have technical knowledge that you need to know everything about an application before hosting it. You will use templates modules made by others, just install them and make it works, for you, your friends or your company. Then, only when problems occurs you'll need to do some research and understand how it works, but your first installation only took minutes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h3 class="text-muted text-center">Our ultimate goal is to keep the Internet how is was originally designed :</h3>
              <h2 class="text-center">A distributed network, where each peer is the equal to the others.</h2>
              <h4 style="text-align: center;">For this, we need to standardize the way we host open-source applications.</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_blue_light">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 mb0">
              <h1 class="text-center">For who?</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_blue_light mt0 mb0">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <img alt="Odoo - Sample 1 for three columns" class="img img-rounded img-responsive" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/friends.jpg" style=""/>
              <h4 class="mt16">Friends</h4>
              <p>You have some technical knowledge, you want to promote open-source software to your friends but you know maintaining it will be a nightmare?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <img alt="Odoo - Sample 2 for three columns" class="img img-rounded img-responsive" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/compagnies.jpg" style=""/>
              <h4 class="mt16">Compagnies</h4>
              <p>You want a reliable, secure infrastructure with powerful and controllable softwares for your company, but only one employee have technical skills?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <img alt="Odoo - Sample 3 for three columns" class="img img-rounded img-responsive" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/hosters.jpg" style="animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
              <h4 class="mt16">Hosters</h4>
              <p>You want to help the others who don't have enough time or technical knowledge, and gain your life thanks to it?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_blue_light mt0">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 mt0 mb16">
              <h3 class="text-center">Clouder will help you build a reliable infrastructure in no time</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mt16 mb16" style="">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt32 mb32">
              <h2>How it works</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <img alt="Odoo CMS - a big picture" class="img img-responsive" src="/clouder_website/static/src/img/library/schema.png" style="margin: 0 auto"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_dark" style="">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h1 class="text-center">Our strengths</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_dark mb0" style="">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row mt16 mb16">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <span class="fa fa-cloud-upload fa-5x" style=""/>
              <h3 class="mt8 mb0">Scalable</h3>
              <div class="text-muted">Easily deploy your applications on a whole infrastructure, not a single server.<br/>
You can use one Clouder to configure your personnal server as well as use it to manage the infrastructures of several companies.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <span class="fa fa-exchange fa-5x" style="animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
              <h3 class="mt8 mb0">Links</h3>
              <div class="text-muted">Links between applications</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
              <span class="fa fa-upload fa-5x" style="animation-play-state: paused; transition: none 0s ease 0s"/>
              <h3 class="mt8 mb0">Platform Agnostic</h3>
              <div class="text-muted">Clouder only take care of the applications, not the server under them.<br/>
This mean you can deploy applications on dedicated servers or virtual machines and manage your network as you want without worries.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="oe_dark">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 mb0 mt0">
              <h3 class="text-center">And the most important</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb16 oe_dark">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row mt16 mb16">
            <div class="text-center col-md-12">
              <span class="fa fa-heart fa-5x"/>
              <h3 class="mt8 mb0">Open-Source</h3>
              <div class="text-muted">You will always own and control your own data, your infrastructure is yours.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="jumbotron mt0 oe_red mb0">
        <div class="container">
          <h2 style="text-align: center;">Join the network</h2>
          <div class="js_follow_alias hidden" data-follow="on" data-id="5" data-object="mail.group">
